    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Requires the Department of Business, Economic Development, and Tourism to study the impacts of disallowing the dividends paid deduction for real estate investment trusts.  Requires a report to the Legislature.  Effective 7/1/2050.  (SD1)"
    }
